# Design System (Acctual)

Before producing any UI code, restyling work, or visual change in this repo, apply the Acctual design system from `DS/DESIGN (1).md`. Use the CSS variables defined in `app/globals.css` (`--color-*`, `--text-*`, `--radius-*`, `--shadow-*`); never hard-code hex values, generic gray shadows, or sharp corners.

## Quick Color Reference
- text (primary): `#0f0f0f` → `--color-midnight-ink`
- text (secondary/supporting): `#1e1e1e` → `--color-charcoal-whisper`
- text (muted/meta): `#8d8d8d` → `--color-graphite-mute`
- background (canvas): `#f7fafc` → `--color-cool-mist`
- background (cards): `#ffffff` → `--color-paper-white`
- border/hairline: `#afb0b1` → `--color-stone-edge`
- accent (small punctuation only): `#0098f2` → `--color-invoice-blue` (checkmarks, eyebrow tags, inline links)
- primary CTA fill: `#0d111b` → `--color-onyx-button`
- decorative avatars: `#f200ca` → `--color-magenta-tile`, `#6d56fc` → `--color-iris-glow`
- pastel washes (mockup backdrops only): `--color-wash-sky`, `--color-wash-lilac`, `--color-wash-petal`
- repo card surfaces (tune separately): `--color-card-sky|lilac|petal` + matching `-ink`, `-muted`, `-body` tokens in `app/globals.css`

## Typography
- Font: Open Runde via Inter substitute (`--font-open-runde`), weights 400/500/600
- Signature accent: Caveat (`--font-caveat`) — testimonial attributions only, never functional UI
- Body: 16px weight 400, line-height 1.5
- Meta: 14px weight 400–500 Graphite Mute
- Headings: weight 600 Midnight Ink, negative letter-spacing at larger sizes
- Display/hero: 64px weight 600, tracking -2.4px

## Radii
- Cards: 20px (`--radius-cards`)
- Images/illustrations: 32px (`--radius-images`)
- Inputs: 12px (`--radius-inputs`)
- Buttons/pills/tags/chips: 100px (`--radius-buttons`, `--radius-tags`)

## Shadows (subtle black only)
- Cards: `rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 0 2.5px 2.5px` → `--shadow-subtle`
- Primary CTA ring: → `--shadow-subtle-2`

## Layout
- Page max-width: 1200px
- Section gap: 64px
- Card padding: 24px
- Element gap: 16px

## Do
- Keep the UI 99% achromatic — Invoice Blue, Magenta Tile, and Iris Glow appear only as small functional dots
- Use Midnight Ink for primary text — never pure black
- Primary CTA is always Onyx Button pill with `--shadow-subtle-2` — no second filled button color
- Use 20px radius on cards, 100px on buttons, 32px on masked images
- Separate sections with whitespace and alternating Cool Mist bands, not heavy borders
- Use Stone Edge for hairline dividers only

## Don't
- Don't use Invoice Blue, Magenta Tile, or Iris Glow as large fills or section backgrounds
- Don't add hover-lift shadows or colored glows — cards use `--shadow-subtle` only
- Don't use `#000000` for text
- Don't use sharp corners (0–4px) on cards or buttons
- Don't use Signal Blue / cord.com tokens (legacy — removed)
- Don't use Caveat in buttons, links, or labels
